Interface IContextResolver

All Known Subinterfaces:
IDocumentContextResolver, IDOMContextResolver, IMetadataContextResolver, ISymbolContextResolver, ITaglibContextResolver, IWorkspaceContextResolver
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractContextResolver, AbstractDocumentContextResolver, AbstractSymbolContextResolver, CachingSymbolContextResolver
public interface IContextResolver

Super type of all context resolvers. May be sub-classed but should not be implemented directly. Use AbstractContextResolver to implement.
